                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>\n                <date>February 25<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1847</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I embrace the opportunity of the departure<lb/> of my friend\n                    <persName>Mr Alex Guthrie</persName> (to whom allow<lb/> me to present you) to\n                forward you amt I have<lb/> collected for you as pr a/c enclosed the 4 citrons<lb/>\n                were sent by a friend of yours during your indisposition<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Gutheim</persName> wishes to be considered a subscribing<lb/> member to\n                the Publication Society, the Hebrew Inst.<lb/> the same, subscription being\n                    <sic>forwared</sic> for the past<lb/> and current year you will please forward\n                the books<lb/> to meet as usual for the Institute I have yet to<lb/> collect some\n                more subscriptions for you <persName>Mr Lindo</persName><lb/> says he is indebted\n                for 3 years only he having paid<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Pike</persName> one years amt. <persName>Mr Jonas</persName> thinks\n                you<lb/> ought not to charge him for his fathers obituary<lb/> I hope you have\n                recovered your health<lb/> I am my self quite unwell a severe nervous affection<lb/>\n                rendering study or close application extremely painful<lb/> I am compelled to forego\n                therefore most of my<lb/> correspondence for the present I will answer<lb/> your\n                friendly letter however shortly in the mean<lb/> time believe me yours Truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Lewis Abraham</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p36h4d98d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
